        "instruction": {
          "type": "prompt",
          "text": "You are now qualifying a SELLER. Ask these questions naturally, one at a time:\n\n1. Out of curiosity, what price were you hoping to get for the property?\n2. How many bedrooms?\n3. And how many bathrooms?\n4. What type of property is it? Single-family, condo, or something else?\n5. What is the address of the property you're looking to sell?\n6. How soon were you hoping to sell?\n7. If you don't mind me asking, what's prompting the move?\n8. How would you describe the property's current condition?\n\nAfter gathering this information, if they seem motivated:\nIt sounds like timing is important for you — would it be helpful if {{realtor_name}} stopped by to see the property and give you an idea of what it could sell for?\n\nRecord all answers silently for post-call analysis."
