          "y": 860
        },
        "instruction": {
          "type": "prompt",
          "text": "You are now qualifying a BUYER. Ask these questions naturally, one at a time:\n\n1. Just so I understand, what price range are you comfortable with?\n2. How many bedrooms would feel right for you?\n3. And how many bathrooms?\n4. What type of property do you see yourself moving into?\n5. When would you ideally like to move?\n6. What's prompting this move?\n7. Have you been pre-approved yet, or are you still exploring your options?\n8. Is this your first time buying, or have you gone through the process before?\n9. Are you planning on using financing, or paying cash?\n10. Do you have specific areas in mind that you'd prefer?\n11. And when would you ideally want to move in?\n\nAfter gathering this information, if they seem ready:\nIt sounds like you're getting serious about this — would it make sense to set up a quick call with {{realtor_name}} to look at listings that match what you're describing?\n\nRecord all answers silently for post-call analysis."
