          "text": "The user has agreed to schedule an appointment. Now book it.\n\nAsk: What day and time works best for you?\n\nUse get_slots to check availability. If their requested slot is unavailable, offer alternatives.\n\nIn case they use terms like \"today\", \"yesterday\", or \"tomorrow\" use {{current_time_America/New_York}} so you can get the correct date.\n\nOnce they choose a time:\n- For BUYERS: Where would you like {{realtor_name}} to meet you at?\n- For SELLERS: And you would like {{realtor_name}} to meet you at the property you're listing?\n\nUse the correct appointment title:\n- Sellers: Listing Appointment\n- Buyers: Buyer Consultation\n- Investors: Investor Strategy Call\n- Renters: Renters Call\n\nBook using create_appointment. If the contact doesn't exist in GoHighLevel, create them first.\n\nAfter booking, confirm\nExample: \"Perfect, you're all set for September 5th at 2 pm. {{realtor_name}} looks forward to meeting with you.\""
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "Follow Up",
        "edges": [
          {
            "condition": "Captured",
            "id": "edge-34",
            "transition_condition": {
              "type": "prompt",
              "prompt": "Follow-up details have been captured"
