        "id": "node-follow-up",
        "type": "conversation",
        "display_position": {
          "x": 3850,
          "y": 2210
        },
        "instruction": {
          "type": "prompt",
          "text": "The user cannot or doesn't want to book now but may be open to follow-up.\n\nAsk: Totally understood. When would be a good time for me to follow up with you?\n\nThen ask: And how would you prefer I reach out — call or text?\n\nKeep it conversational. After gathering the follow-up details, confirm: Got it, I'll make a note of that and we'll reach out then."
        }
      },
